nning p\u00e5 masterniv\u00e5. Vi er spesialister p\u00e5 kvinnehelse, og vi er vant til \u00e5 tenke helhetlig. Jeg er sikker p\u00e5 at jordm\u00f8dre vil gi et godt tilbud, sier Dalseg."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f0c0b807526f1b3d1e28df7673f97db1437cc4e759e23927a44ec64805757b7c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-06T03:50:04.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Fastlegene i Trondheim mobiliserer n\u00e5 kraftig mot forslaget om at jordm\u00f8dre skal f\u00e5 et st\u00f8rre ansvar for kvinnehelsen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article14554496.ece/1bcfnx/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS_fastlege12.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a90fda29cd8072586f930e35b95e5bd843f78b64.jpg?59646d7d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Kjemper om kvinners underliv -adressa.no", "Svekke kvaliteten", "Hele pasienten", "Kvinnelig lege", "- Foretrekker jordmor"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "a90fda29cd8072586f930e35b95e5bd843f78b64"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Fastlege", "H\u00f8yre", "Helse"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Fastlege,H\u00f8yre,Helse"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "vinmonopolet"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kvinne", "kvinnelig lege", "jordmor", "lege"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["helse", "h\u00f8yre", "trondheims 165", "ingvill dalseg", "risvollan", "h\u00f8yrepolitiker"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "oppdal"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "aage bjertn\u00e6s"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", "pluss/nyheter"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/plu